OL,3,CSwimming facility announces closure
OL,4,Cafter funding crisis
OL,6,FA trustee of a swimming pool facility
OL,7,Fsays its imminent closure is a
OL,8,F"tragedy for the town" following the
OL,9,Flocal council's decision to stop
OL,10,Ffunding the centre.
OL,12,FThe Scottish Borders Council decided
OL,13,Fagainst granting #80,000 to help
OL,14,FJedburgh Leisure Facilities Trust
OL,15,F(JLFT) keep its doors open until March
OL,16,F2025.
