OL,3,CSwimming facility announces closure
OL,4,Cafter funding crisis
OL,6,FCouncillors rejected the motion at a
OL,7,FFull Council meeting on 28 November
OL,8,F2024. The Scottish Borders Council
OL,9,Fprovided the Trust with #40,000 of
OL,10,Femergency funding in August 2024.
OL,12,FJLFT say their financial issues result
OL,13,Ffrom high energy costs, the impact of
OL,14,Fthe pandemic and an inadequate heating
OL,15,Fsystem.
