OL,3,CSwimming facility announces closure
OL,4,Cafter funding crisis
OL,6,FRuth Dorward, Co-Chair of JLFT, says
OL,7,Fshe's "devastated" for the local
OL,8,Fcommunity. She said: "I'm devastated
OL,9,Ffor Laidlaw Memorial Pool and all our
OL,10,Fusers. I'm also devastated for our
OL,11,Fstaff, some of whom have been with us
OL,12,Ffor decades.
OL,14,F"This is a tragedy. It's a tragedy for
OL,15,Fthe staff. It's a tragedy for the
OL,16,Ftown. And I think it's a very short-
OL,17,Fsighted decision."
