OL,3,CSwimming facility announces closure
OL,4,Cafter funding crisis
OL,6,FThe leisure centre is currently in
OL,7,Fdebt of more than #50,000, and only
OL,8,Fhas #20,000 to cover its bills in
OL,9,FDecember 2024. JLFT's last day open to
OL,10,Fthe public is 29 November 2024.
OL,12,FDuring the discussion in council,
OL,13,Fcouncillors voiced their concerns
OL,14,Fabout the financial issues moving
OL,15,Fforward after already granting #40,000
OL,16,Fa few months ago.
OL,18,FThe Scottish Borders Council have
OL,19,Foverspent by #4m for the financial
OL,20,Fyear of 2024-25.
